Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:04.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,470)}School Rumble is coming up next, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:10.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Second year, class C, Shigeo Umezu,\Nmember of the track and field team, 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a girlfriend\Nhe’s just begun seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:17.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka Kido, also on\Nthe track and field team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:19.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They began seeing each other in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:23.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a favorable beginning.\NHowever, he had a concern…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:27.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t kiss her… Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:30.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chance after chance…\NI just cannot kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:33.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:35.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, today is the athletic meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:38.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll show off how good I am and\Nwhen the excitement is at its highest…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:40.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and see, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:43.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surely win this race. And I’ll…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:45.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,… kiss—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a pig! A pig’s running wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:54.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeo’s been hit by a pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:00.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Shigeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:01.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:02.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:04.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped, it was the pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:09.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t say it that I wanted to make\Na good showing and then kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:11.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll make up for it, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:15.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are strong, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:17.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:20.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So… I have a request of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:24.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I come in first, as a reward,\Nwill you kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:32.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been troubled by it\Nall this time, and she just…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:34.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:37.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you’re sure to come in first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it’s not a reward or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:46.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,After Madoka gave me this chance,\NI’m giving it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it supposed to be a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:56.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I’ll have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:58.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it’s my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:04.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say… women are…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:06.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Women are…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Napoleon?! What are you doing here?!
