Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve seen all those who were\Nhurt in the cavalry battle…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s still someone left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:22.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get hurt during\Nthe cavalry battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um… I did get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:44.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I thought I’d just\Ncome get a compress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But just for that, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you hesitated\Ncoming in just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to worry\Nabout something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t you just show me the wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be running in the\Nrelay next, won’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:00.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I should take care of it accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re different from\Nwhen we first met, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:16.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn’t remember… that? None of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn’t even see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:27.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I pushed Hario down in here,\Nyou happened to be present then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hario?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that would make him\Nlook like a pervert, wouldn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an accident, just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:38.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn’t seen him for a\Nwhile and I got so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… why Hario?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was Harima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:45.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, it’s an old habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:51.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you and Harima-kun know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:54.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:06:00.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s hard to explain our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:09.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was the landlady and\Nhe was the tenant, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:13.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said… Don’t let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? Jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:32.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking!\NI was just curious, that’s all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If there’s something going on between the school’s infamous delinquent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:38.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the new beautiful nurse, anyone would be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:43.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a good one.\NIt sounds indecent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going back. It’s almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What about your injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take this compress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you’re alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:05.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly kind, aren’t you?\NBut you needn’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:13.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is the relay race between classes,\NSecond year Girls’ Division!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:18.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this close competition!\NClass C: 220 points, Class D: 218 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,On your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The turning point of the battle\Nis the relay race.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It holds the key to the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And they’re off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan! Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:45.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the lead is Class C!\NThe gap grows wider!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:49.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The second runner is already on her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Class C’s Kozue Mihara is fast! Very fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, they can\Nshake free from Class D!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Harima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:10.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got hurt because that pig ran about during the 100-meter race and crashed into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it only natural that you\Ntake my place in the relay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:17.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it hurt, Napoleon? Were you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are listening to me, Harima?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you’ve got to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. I won’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, why are you\Nkeeping the pig at school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll tell on you, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:36.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it’s a pig or a giraffe,\Nwhere I keep it is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:44.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Class C’s Megumi Sagano is still on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth runner is Eri Sawachika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Class C is up there all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not going to let anyone\Nget the better of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Runner Sawachika is fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Contrary to that beautiful figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, perhaps the magnificent\Nrunning is because of the figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawachika-san is tremendous, isn’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri-chan is usually faster…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:27.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She hurt her leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Sawachika-san fall in an odd way during the cavalry battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:36.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hario… Harima-kun, you were\Non the same team, weren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She came to the infirmary earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:44.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it wasn’t that bad,\Nbut it’s been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be… when she…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It has nothing to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She went and shaved off my beard!\NServes her right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that so, Napoleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to feed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:12.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it really hurts.\NI can’t stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit more…\NMy legs are heavy…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not make it… but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don’t want to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The baton! Where’s the baton!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:39.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The baton…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be okay, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri-chan, I was so worried.\NAre you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:01.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let’s go watch the boys’ relay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s going to start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:08.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll stay here for a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be along soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:16.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rich Girl… I’ll win… for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re even after that! Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
