Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the final event of this meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The boys’ relay begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In the second year division,\NClass D is on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And five points behind is Class C.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:10.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,For us to win, we have\Nto take first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be okay, we’ll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a penalty game if we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:18.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The heroic gladiators are\Nnow entering the arena!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:26.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:29.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Miko-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Make up for what you did\Nin the cavalry battle, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:37.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I didn’t do it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re going to keep\Nholding that over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:40.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for protecting me\Nfrom Harry’s kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:49.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll give me a kiss\Nif we win?! Miko-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I say that?! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:13:00.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m rooting for you!\NPlease do your best, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:01.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sara…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! That’s sneaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:08.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you become close, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How come all the girls only call to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo-kun is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Shadow Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:21.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo-kun is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:26.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at the slack\Nfaces on those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:30.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They don’t look ready for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you guys okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no sense of readiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on with Class C?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason the morale\Nof the troops is disturbed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How fragile they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:45.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Women are specters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They are fools after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:52.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought they were good competitors,\Nbut it seems I overestimated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:04.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember! The relay is different\Nfrom individual short-distance races!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:08.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m giving you a plan for certain victory,\Nso listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,In a relay, the handing of\Nthe baton decides everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:15.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing of the handoff\Nmust be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:18.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what I was just going to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re pretty knowledgeable\Nabout it, aren’t you, Imadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The relay will redeem us from\Nthe dishonor of the cavalry battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to say that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:30.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can be serious\Nabout things sometimes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:33.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win, we’ll be heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima, we’re counting\Non you to be the anchor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you’re talking to, dumb ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Easily… easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:46.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,On your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They start all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s fast! As you’d expect from Class D!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:14.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this unknown runner is a grade above!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Class D is on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:16.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is… Class C has passed the baton!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:25.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast! Runner Asou is running vehemently!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He overtook the top runner in seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:37.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Imadori is in a crouching start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was stupid to have believed in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:41.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What “hey,” you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:44.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:45.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He suddenly began tumbling!\NA grand tumbling display!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, he’s started to run!\NIs this part of some plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that? I started\Nwith tumbling to build up speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:15:59.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s called special rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:00.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s been overtaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s been overtaken!\NA great miscalculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:05.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,With this lead, we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:12.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,With me and Harry left…\NIt’s a shoo in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tougou, don’t underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:20.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Us? You’re placing a lot of confidence in Harima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t make me wait.\NI’m not so patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:29.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori’s finally arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will exert myself as much as I can, Imadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Special rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:39.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Runner Hanai’s yell is tremendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s taken on the look of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind god has swooped down upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:52.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be! He’s…\NHanai’s closing the gap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s putting pressure… on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:02.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay! We’re still leading!\NI’m up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:03.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:05.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:12.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A come-from-behind win is\Nthe most impressive kind of win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:17.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come after me, Japanese Samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This hairstyle is a defeated soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:22.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:26.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! What if the cap\Nfalls off while I’m running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.73,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:29.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:34.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it! Our manly spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:39.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Four-Eyes, you really don’t think\Nof people’s feelings, do you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:41.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:43.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima intends to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun’s fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my mind about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s happening?\NYou really are doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:58.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s great, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s getting applause\Nfrom the other classes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a second faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:05.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to reach the goal\Nbefore the cap falls off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I run, the more it slips back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:17.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,God, please… this is the\Nfirst time I’m praying…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me… a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji Harima is first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Class C wins the championship!
