Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.88,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy100\fsp-1\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnImpact\fs72\b0\i0\c&H1A16DF&\pos(503,119)}{\fscy112}F{\fscy88}ansub
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.88,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.2\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs26\i1\c&HAE690B&\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\fscy115\pos(501,135)}www.mokkori.cz
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:04.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,After the battle, you are\Na valuable school friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I have to pair up with a guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the only duty of the committee chairman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:15.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m surprised at how delicate you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see… where’s Karasuma-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:38.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun is in charge of the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re all acting like\Nthey haven’t noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dancing the Oklahoma Mixer so enjoyably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:05.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I won’t have to hide my head anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:08.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’m back to being all alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:13.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, that matches me, the delinquent, best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Rich Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,With that leg of yours… and me, bald…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:30.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re dancing with me,\Nso you should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:40.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rich Girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m okay… I’m fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:58.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is special…\NIt’s special, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawachika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:28.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Beard…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dancing sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:54.33,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:22:00.09,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:04.79,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:10.26,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:14.88,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:17.55,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:20.94,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:23.79,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:28.23,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:31.37,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:34.56,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:40.57,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.58,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.49,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:50.47,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:09.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is a person’s fate governed\Nby money or chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.51,0:23:12.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the perpetual mystery\Nthat surrounds the seas of the time.
